title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Anandi's father gets arrested for the weapons found in his fields.Mahavir meets Bhairon and Basant, he warns them that anyone who is related to their family would be a victim of their rivalry.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Khajaan Singh is a victim of a high profile rivalry. He is taken to Jaipur for an enquiry.Anandi is emotional about her father being arrested. But, Sumitra manages to handle the situation.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Anandi's mother is depressed because of her husband's arrest and she being helpless. Meanwhile, Mahavir plans his next step against Kalyani Devi and her family.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Bhairon Singh brings Bhagwati to his house. Dadisa gets angry and gives sarcastic comments. Bhagwati hears Dadisa talking about Khajaan Singh's case and his conviction.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Dadisa, Bhairon and Basant discuss Khajaan Singh's case and later, Dadisa scolds Anandi for handing Nandu over to her mother, as she is infected. Afterwards, Jaggu asks Sumitra to sing him a lullaby him like Anandi used to do.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Dadisa tells Basant to keep an account of the money that is being spent on Anandi's father, Khajaan. Later, Dadisa yells at Jagdish for bringing Anandi's relative, Phooli to their house.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Kalyani Devi humiliates Khajaan's wife and Anandi consoles her mother. An old lady named Lachi reveals that Mahavir Singh's only son is still alive and is with Kalyani Devi.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Shyam asks for permission from his mother to change the window of his new room. Mahavir Singh visits Kalyani and reveals her secret.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Everyone is shocked when Mahavir Singh reveals that Basant is his son and he wants to take him back. Dadisa keeps completely quiet when Mahavir reveals Basant is his son and Basant wonders about Dadisa's silence.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Dharamveer is worried as Dadisa is not speaking to anyone. Basant threatens to commit suicide if Dadisa doesn't tell him the truth. Dadisa tells Basant that he is Mahavir Singh's son.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Basant questions Dadisa about why she lied to him, Dadisa shows Basant the picture of his real mother and reveals that Basant's real mother wanted to keep it as a secret before dying.
